ah today i was remenincsing about things in the past.when i began to remember of my childhood. i will tell u what i remembered now. it was about 13 years ago now when i had realized how curious i can be. it was in the evening time of the day a little before dinner time. when it happened. i was sitting on the couch watching my mom clip her toenails with the big toenail clipper(at least it seemed big to me back then). i dont know why but i just couldnt stop staring at her feet because they were just so crusty. i mean cruuuuuuuuuuuuussssssssty and the toenail pieces were sharp you could cut someone with them(ok maybe i am exaggerratting a bit about the toenaiil being that sharp). so she eventually stop clipping her toenails and went into the kitchen. i sat for awhile staring at the toenail clipper. it was hypnotic. i picked it up and all of a sudden out of nowhere a thought came a cross my head. that thought was what will happen if i clip the cord that plugs the lamp into the wall. i wanted to know really really bad. so i clipped it and i got electrocuted. it was i dont know weird and crazy. like the light bulb exploded and  some other stuff happened too. it was a life altering experience u could say nah not really. i just hope i wont do it again. so this was a tale of thomas more will be available in a later time.

so today was okay.i went to the zoo for the first time in my whole life. it was actually pretty fun well at least more fun then i thought it was gonna be. i saw all sorts of animals. most of them was really annoying like the birds. but it was still fun though. i saw a gorilla for the first time in real life. it was cool. i saw the cutest little monkeys at least i think they were monkeys i dont really know actually. well let me start from the beginning of the day. so i woke up at 9:30 only cuz my nephew woke me by playing with my eyes for some reason. i swear that  kid is crazy. then we (me, my sister=destiny, and nephew=khalil) went to walmart to buy some film for our camera. we did then we went to get our other sister camisha. then we went to wendys and ate something. next we went to the zoo. the first thing we saw was these birds i forgot what they were called. all i know is that they were multicolored. then we went to the primates. we saw all kinds of monkeys like the black hand spider monkey, orangutan, baboon,(damn that thing is ugly) and the gorilla. we also saw a cotton top tamarin and pygmy. then we went to where the elephant was. there we saw an elephant, rhino, hippo, and a manned wolf(aint even a wolf it is like a fox with stilts). we saw some cheetahs. we went to the savannah next and saw giraffeas(sorry cant spell that for some reason), gazzell(which is a mini antelope), ostrich,meercat, palla cat, fennec,white bengal tiger,red panda bear,indochinese tiger(which may i add was being a real bitch because everytime that it saw me it would turn around and leave and hide), a lion and a lemur. i went to birds side and i saw a lot of really annoying birds. i saw an macaw. i almost got ate up by a swan i dont know why it wanted to eat me i guess it thought i might taste good or something.i saw a flamingo it was cool. i went to the reptiles side and saw some pretty cool things as well. the cool things that i saw was the komodo dragon, bearded dragon, and the egyptian cobra. i saw some other snkes too but they were not as cool at least that is what i think like an anaconda, a python , king cobra, and a rattlesnake. we saw some aligators. we went to the petting zoo area and i saw a llama, sheep, goat, and chicken. then we left and i was really tired because my feet was sore. then we took khalil home a day earlier because his mom called. we took him and i went to chickfila and got some nuggets and ate them. i went home and watched some televison and thats it. oh yeah we took lots and lots of pictures while we were at the zoo.i even took some for my cell phone. so overall i had a lot of fun today.and maybe one day i might even go to the zoo more often.

today after i finshed talking to kacee and watching vh1. so i was really really bored right. right. so i didnt have nothing to do so i got bored when all of a sudden a thought came acrossed my mind. that thought was i should make a powerpoint. a powerpoint about what u may ask. a powerpoint about dreams. now u might be thinking well why in hell would someone just randomly decide to make a powerpoint about dreams. well u know what i am gonna tell u i did the powerpoint on dreams because before school got out in my english class we had to write an expository essay on any topic of our chosing. i chose to write about dreams. i did and i got a good grade on the essay at least i think so anyway. but enough about that i crreated a powerpoint right. in working on the creation of this powerpoint i look onto the research i gathered when i wrote my expository essay. i also turned to another important resource that source is google. yes its great i can find just about anything on google. so i turned to this resource because there were a few things that i needed to know for my powerpoint so it could be complete and expand it. i needed to know of some different types of dreams and i needed in detail information of some known sleep disorders.now in picking out what types of dreams i was going to put in my powerpoint i had to chose between a few that i knew that wasnt going to spark my curiosity into making me want to further learn more and more about the subject. so i found five different types of dreams that i was okay to put in my powerpoint. the five types are ordinary, lucid, telepathic, premonitory, and nightmares. and i also added three sleep disorders to my powerpoint. they are sleep walking, sleep talking, and sleep paralysis. now i could go into detail about everything that i put into my powerpoint but that would defeat the whole purpose of me making it so i will not go into detail about what i put into my powerpoint. plus i am too lazy to do all of that typing all over again. NOW OK FOR EVERY PERSON WHO HAS READ THIS ENTRY I AM IN NEED OF YOUR ASSISTANCE. I HAVE NO CLUE ON WHAT COLORS MY BACKGROUND IS GOING TO BE.
